container_info.post_install_tip: Add data to your sheet -- use column headers and enter a few valid rows. From the menu, choose “Add-ons > AppSheet > Launch” and click "PREPARE" and "GO" in the sidebar. Your browser opens the AppSheet site and an app is auto-created from your sheet.

name: AppSheet
description: Build a custom mobile app from your Google spreadsheet. It is easy, takes only a few minutes, and no coding is involved.
